## 7. Out of Scope

These are explicitly not being built. If this list shrinks, flag it as a scope change.

- Automated data integrations (Google Sheets, CRM, Eventbrite) — manual entry only in v1
- Custom report builder or additional templates beyond board and funder
- Multi-organization / multi-tenant support
- AI-generated narrative — ED Notes is a free-text field, not AI-drafted
- Donor-facing portals or client-facing views
- Budget / expense tracking — finance system is separate
- Automated email or SMS deadline alerts — user must open the dashboard
- Mobile native app — web-responsive browser is sufficient
- For-profit companies, large NGOs, government orgs, activist or pure advocacy organizations
- Staff editing previously submitted metric entries

