## Report Template Specs

### Board Report — section order
1. Organization name, report period, date generated
2. ED Notes (free-text field, max 300 words — optional)
3. Program Outcomes — one section per active program: metric name, target, actual, status flag
4. Fundraising Summary — revenue by category (grant / donation / other), target vs. actual, overall status
5. Funder Deadlines — all active funders sorted by next deadline date (ascending). Deadline window colouring applies (red/amber/yellow for ≤90 days); funders beyond 90 days are listed without a colour flag. **Intentional:** the board sees the full funder calendar, not just what is imminent.

### Funder Report — section order
1. Organization name, funder name, report period, date generated
2. ED Notes (free-text field, max 300 words — optional)
3. Program Outcomes — one section per program linked to this funder: metric name, target, actual, status flag
4. Funding Summary — revenue entries for this funder, target vs. actual
5. Next Deadline — renewal date and report due date for this funder

